=== Decision rule check (TL must drop LESS than MLP under transfer) ===
  count N=1     : TL drop=-3.1pp | MLP h=64 drop=-3.7pp | MLP h=128 drop=-4.0pp | MLP h=256 drop=-4.1pp  → TL does NOT transfer better
  count N=3     : TL drop=+3.4pp | MLP h=64 drop=+4.1pp | MLP h=128 drop=+3.9pp | MLP h=256 drop=+4.9pp  → TL transfers BETTER
  count N=4     : TL drop=+5.0pp | MLP h=64 drop=+6.5pp | MLP h=128 drop=+6.7pp | MLP h=256 drop=+7.9pp  → TL transfers BETTER
  occ shift TL  : TL drop=+5.0pp | MLP h=64 drop=+9.0pp | MLP h=128 drop=+9.7pp | MLP h=256 drop=+10.5pp  → TL transfers BETTER
  occ shift BR  : TL drop=+4.0pp | MLP h=64 drop=+7.8pp | MLP h=128 drop=+8.1pp | MLP h=256 drop=+8.8pp  → TL transfers BETTER
